289
00:20:55,130 --> 00:20:57,230
Ji An had indigestion before she came.

290
00:20:58,230 --> 00:20:59,970
It seems like she is not feeling well.

291
00:21:01,030 --> 00:21:03,400
I think she will be fine after a short break.

292
00:21:03,870 --> 00:21:04,870
No.

293
00:21:05,540 --> 00:21:07,840
