295
00:21:10,010 --> 00:21:11,750
Gosh. - Well, that...

296
00:21:12,580 --> 00:21:13,880
The director knew about her.

297
00:21:15,080 --> 00:21:16,150
What?

298
00:21:17,680 --> 00:21:19,820
Oh, this is really too much.

299
00:21:19,990 --> 00:21:21,050
Gosh.

300
00:21:21,660 --> 00:21:22,760
You arrange that. - Okay.

301
00:21:25,230 --> 00:21:26,630
We will take a short break from filming.

302
00:21:41,140 --> 00:21:43,240
You read the script, and conveyed the emotions to me, right?

303
00:21:45,380 --> 00:21:46,580
You didn't do it half-heartedly, right?

304
00:21:47,150 --> 00:21:48,150
You did it properly, right?

305
00:21:48,680 --> 00:21:49,680
I did it properly.

306
00:21:50,320 --> 00:21:52,950
Just like we have always done.

307
00:21:54,090 --> 00:21:56,020
