314
00:22:16,810 --> 00:22:18,040
So, like a reversal.

315
00:22:19,610 --> 00:22:20,910
A reversal?

316
00:22:21,720 --> 00:22:23,619
Simply put, now,

317
00:22:23,620 --> 00:22:25,950
