319
00:22:40,200 --> 00:22:41,640
Today's filming has been cancelled.

320
00:22:41,840 --> 00:22:42,840
You can go home.

321
00:22:46,440 --> 00:22:47,710
Removed from the show?

322
00:22:48,210 --> 00:22:50,010
I'm sorry. That's just how it turned out.

323
00:22:50,380 --> 00:22:51,509
Even so, notifying her of being removed...

324
00:22:51,510 --> 00:22:53,210
