427
00:28:43,600 --> 00:28:46,100
Especially a top star like Ji An.

428
00:28:47,100 --> 00:28:48,100
You are smart.

429
00:28:49,100 --> 00:28:50,169
You are right.

430
00:28:50,170 --> 00:28:51,400
But that is...

431
