433
00:28:56,710 --> 00:29:00,880
And since her contract had ended, it was legally ambiguous.

434
00:29:02,980 --> 00:29:03,980
Contract ended?

435
00:29:04,420 --> 00:29:05,449
Yes. Her contract...

436
00:29:05,450 --> 00:29:07,319
