Oh my, look at her.

462
00:30:46,420 --> 00:30:48,190
Are you crying? - You didn't see it, did you?

463
00:30:49,960 --> 00:30:52,360
Yes, Ji An must be devastated.

464
00:30:54,060 --> 00:30:55,360
