471
00:31:09,180 --> 00:31:10,180
What the hell are you talking about?

472
00:31:13,580 --> 00:31:15,420
Woof woof, happy now?

473
00:31:17,450 --> 00:31:18,450
You crazy jerk.

474
00:31:19,450 --> 00:31:21,289
So, Ji An did...

475
00:31:21,290 --> 00:31:23,160
